---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="DualTone - Design System from One Color" description="One HEX, full design system. 40+ tokens, light + dark mode, WCAG auto-fix. Free.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="mt-8 mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">DualTone</span></h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Design System from One Color</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          One color in. Full design system out. Enter a single HEX color and get a complete palette: 11-shade primary scale, neutral scale, semantic tokens, light mode, dark mode — all WCAG-checked. Production-ready in 10 seconds.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">40+ Design Tokens</strong> — primary scale, neutral scale, semantic tokens from one HEX</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Light + Dark Mode</strong> — both themes from one source color, split-view</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">WCAG Auto-Fix</strong> — contrast checker with AA/AAA badges, one-tap fix</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Code Export</strong> — CSS Custom Properties, SwiftUI Colors, Tailwind Config, JSON Tokens</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Free, Offline</strong> — no account, no ads, no internet needed</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">DualTone is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">All data on device. No server, no cloud, no analytics.</p>
        <a href="/apps/huecraft/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:support@mdk.guru" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">support@mdk.guru</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
